From: Richard Elberger <rich@richelberger.com>
Subject: [PATCH] fc_deps.json: use commit hash for gg_sdk instead of tag

Kirkstone requires fixed commit hashes for SRCREV. Update fc_deps.json
to use the commit hash that tag v0.4.1 points to.

Upstream-Status: Inappropriate [kirkstone-specific]

diff --git a/fc_deps.json b/fc_deps.json
index 1234567..abcdefg 100644
--- a/fc_deps.json
+++ b/fc_deps.json
@@ -10,7 +10,7 @@
   },
   "gg_sdk": {
     "url": "https://github.com/aws-greengrass/aws-greengrass-component-sdk.git",
-    "rev": "v0.4.1",
+    "rev": "9487b56479ebc20a67bb9dce9b3a3dfb58f91cb9",
     "hash": "sha256-M6FBC01oipl/HgFVoU09pHSsh2zyoEgyijrSUbzmF6g="
   }
 }
